    <title ixia_locid="1" class="- topic/title ">Controller Nodes and High Availability</title>
    <shortdesc ixia_locid="2" class="- topic/shortdesc ">Services in the controller nodes run constantly in active/standby mode
        to provide continuity in the event of a controller failure.</shortdesc>
    <prolog class="- topic/prolog ">
        <author ixia_locid="3" class="- topic/author ">Pedro Sanchez</author>
    </prolog>
    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
        <p ixia_locid="4" class="- topic/p ">Controller services are organized internally into the following groups:</p>
